ancient rod.drops: Dropped by Goblin King. Fished up in City River.

attack potion.drops: Alchemy recipe: 1 Empty Vial, 1 Akomeric, 1 Birds Nest.

cauldron.drops: Dropped by Jin. Found while making Super Defence Potions.

chefs hat.drops: Thieving from the Cook with Cooking skill cape equipped.

chicken knife.drops: Killing Chickens or Elite Chickens. Found in Farm Chests.

drakes compass.drops: Found while crafting Satchels while wearing Leather Gloves and drinking REGULAR Luck Potions.

drakes diary.drops: Found while crafting Satchels while wearing Leather Gloves and not drinking the correct potion.

extreme power stone.drops: Crafting. Completing Vein Slayer Tasks. Found in Kings Chests.

magic watering can.drops: Killing Elite Chickens while wearing full Leather Armor.

max cape.drops: You can buy this from the Market Trader for 13m coins when you are fully maxed (f2p & premium skills to level 99).

mystery egg.drops: Dropped by Phoenix. Discovered in Island Oasis.

mystic dagger.drops: Completing Lumen Slayer Tasks. Found in Kings Chests.

mystic robe.drops: Round while crafting Dragon Rider Tops.

mystic staff.drops: Killing sheep while Ultimaxed (all 99s and 130s) while chopping Ginkgo Trees.

necklace of attack.drops: During combat while in Attack stance.

necklace of defence.drops: During combat while in Defense stance.

necklace of strength.drops: During combat while in Strength stance.

pickaxe of the gods.drops: Found while mining emeralds with Mining skill cape equipped.

power stone.drops: Found while brewing Power Potions. Found in Kings Chests.

scythe of demeter.drops: Found while harvesting any crop. High crop levels means a higher chance.

super power stone.drops: Dropped by Ghost. Crafting. Found in Kings Chests.

wolfmint.drops: Dropped by: Giant Cave Spider, Fluffy, Spider Queen. Pickpocketing: Traveller. Discovery: Mystery Island, The Other Side. Chests: Nefrit.
